<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

360
00:28:02,470 --> 00:28:03,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa memukulinya.</font>

361
00:28:06,650 --> 00:28:11,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku, meski harus berakhir di penjara,</font>

362
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:13,270
<font color=#FFFF00>aku sungguh ingin membunuh dia.</font>

363
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:21,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sungguh minta maaf.</font>

364
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:26,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau minta maaf?</font>

365
00:28:27,770 --> 00:28:30,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bersyukur memilikimu.</font>

366
00:28:30,740 --> 00:28:32,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau tidak ada...</font>

367
00:28:34,090 --> 00:28:35,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak akan bisa melewati semuanya.</font>

368
00:28:39,370 --> 00:28:41,510
<font color=#FFFF00>So Joon akan baik-baik saja, 'kan?</font>

369
00:28:43,170 --> 00:28:44,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan Ma Rin?</font>

370
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:51,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut dia akan mencari-cari So Joon seperti orang gila.</font>

371
00:29:40,850 --> 00:29:42,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Barusan kereta terakhir.</font>

372
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:15,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi semua ini...</font>

373
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:20,840
<font color=#FFFF00>...So Joon menyiapkannya sebagai jaga-jaga.</font>

374
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:23,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

375
00:30:23,070 --> 00:30:25,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin berkat firasat.</font>

376
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:29,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika terjadi sesuatu pada beliau, saya diminta menyerahkannya pada Anda.</font>

377
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:32,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

378
00:30:32,970 --> 00:30:36,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai beliau kembali nanti,</font>

379
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:40,690
<font color=#FFFF00>beliau menunjuk Direktur Wang sebagai Presdir sementara.</font>

380
00:30:40,690 --> 00:30:44,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Juga, ini rencana operasional untuk perusahaan.</font>

381
00:30:44,690 --> 00:30:46,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai beliau kembali,</font>

382
00:30:46,290 --> 00:30:50,240
<font color=#FFFF00>beliau tidak ingin memulai proyek,
cukup menguatkan fondasi perusahaan.</font>

383
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:54,430
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Intinya, beliau ingin perusahaan tetap aman dan stabil.</i></font>

384
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:58,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah tahu berbahaya.</font>

385
00:31:01,140 --> 00:31:03,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari itu dengan bodohnya dia tetap pergi.</font>

386
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:15,450
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kita bertemu di rumahmu tanggal 3 Desember tahun ini.</i></font>

387
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:18,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada yang ingin kutanyakan padamu.</i></font>

388
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:22,880
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa pun yang terjadi,
hari itu kau harus di rumah.</i></font>

389
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:25,180
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Akan kujelaskan padamu hari itu.</i></font>

390
00:31:43,690 --> 00:31:45,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Ki Doong<i>-ssi</i>.</font>

391
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:47,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku menemukan cara menemui So Joon.</i></font>

392
00:31:47,930 --> 00:31:49,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

393
00:31:49,050 --> 00:31:53,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan So Joon masa kini, sih.
Tapi So Joon tetaplah So Joon.</font>

394
00:31:53,970 --> 00:31:56,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

395
00:31:56,190 --> 00:31:59,010
<font color=#FFFF00><i>So Joon dari masa lalu akan datang.</i></font>

396
00:31:59,010 --> 00:32:00,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia punya janji denganku.</font>

397
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:03,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia janji menemuiku tanggal 3 Desember.</font>

398
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada yang ingin dia tanyakan.</font>

399
00:32:04,950 --> 00:32:06,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Berarti...</font>

400
00:32:07,630 --> 00:32:10,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...So Joon dari masa lalu akan menemuimu besok.</font>

401
00:32:10,790 --> 00:32:14,550
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya, kau bisa menemui dia dan memberitahu semua tentang Kim Yong Jin.</i></font>

402
00:32:14,550 --> 00:32:16,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bisa mencegah tragedi ini.</font>

403
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:18,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Then wouldn't the present change?</font>

404
00:32:19,350 --> 00:32:21,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus menemui So Joon besok.</font>

405
00:32:23,330 --> 00:32:24,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

406
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:42,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kita bisa bicara sebentar?</font>

407
00:32:53,410 --> 00:32:56,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat ini kurang tepat buatku.</font>

408
00:32:56,670 --> 00:32:58,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kita bicara lain waktu?</font>

409
00:32:58,730 --> 00:33:01,270
<font color=#FFFF00>So Joon tidak akan datang.</font>

410
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:07,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kenal So Joon?</font>

411
00:33:10,170 --> 00:33:12,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah lama kenal dengan So Joon.</font>

412
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:15,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak 2009...</font>

413
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:21,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah sangat lama sekali.</font>

414
00:33:24,370 --> 00:33:28,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ada di kereta itu juga.</font>

415
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Di Stasiun Namyeong.</font>

416
00:33:34,730 --> 00:33:37,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melihatmu di sana.</font>

417
00:33:37,430 --> 00:33:41,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sama dengan yang di toko.
1000 won saja sepaket.</font>

418
00:33:41,080 --> 00:33:43,190
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[25 Maret 2009]</i></font>

419
00:33:43,190 --> 00:33:47,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Di toko harganya 3000 won,
tapi saya jual 1000 saja.</font>

420
00:33:47,290 --> 00:33:48,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan dilihat.</font>

421
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:50,200
<font color=#FFFF00>- <i>Ahjussi...
</i>- Ya?</font>

422
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Beri aku tiga.</font>

423
00:33:51,250 --> 00:33:52,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Tiga set?</font>

424
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:56,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

425
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:58,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kembaliannya tidak usah.</font>

426
00:33:59,100 --> 00:34:02,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, tidak.
Saya tidak bisa menerimanya.</font>

427
00:34:02,930 --> 00:34:05,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya ini pedagang.
Silakan digunakan.</font>

428
00:34:06,090 --> 00:34:07,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak perlu kembalian.</font>

429
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:12,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tiga buah hanya 1000 won, bisa dipakai menggosok punggung juga.</font>

430
00:34:13,240 --> 00:34:16,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo semuanya. Maaf mengganggu.</font>

431
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:19,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya membawa sikat gigi hebat ini.</font>

432
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:21,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya 1000 won 3 buah.</font>

433
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memotretku?</font>

434
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Biasanya satu buah saja 1000 won.</font>

435
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:25,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Barusan kau memotretku.</font>

436
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:28,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa juga aku melakukannya?</font>

437
00:34:28,270 --> 00:34:29,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau memotretku diam-diam?</font>

438
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak memotretmu, kok.</font>

439
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:33,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan ponselmu padaku.</font>

440
00:34:33,090 --> 00:34:35,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan, sih? Ini punyaku.</font>

441
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:37,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin tahu! Tunjukkan!</font>

442
00:34:37,170 --> 00:34:38,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau aneh sekali.</font>

443
00:34:39,010 --> 00:34:41,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, dia Bap Soon, 'kan?</font>

444
00:34:42,490 --> 00:34:44,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

445
00:34:47,370 --> 00:34:49,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita keluar dan memastikannya!</font>

446
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:52,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirmu aku takut?</font>

447
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:54,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma Rin...</font>

448
00:34:55,250 --> 00:34:57,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma Rin! Ma Rin-<i>ah...</i></font>

449
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:03,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

450
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:07,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan? Berikan ponselmu!</font>

451
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:11,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa juga aku memotret seseorang yang tidak kukenal?</font>

452
00:35:11,470 --> 00:35:12,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melihatnya!</font>

453
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:15,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau melakukannya diam-diam.</font>

454
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:18,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa menunjukkannya, cuma tidak mau saja!</font>

455
00:35:18,690 --> 00:35:20,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membuatku jengkel.</font>

456
00:35:20,770 --> 00:35:22,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Wajahmu kentara jelas kau melakukannya!</font>

457
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Hapus sekarang!</font>

458
00:35:25,990 --> 00:35:28,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Rupanya orang-orang aneh memang ada.</font>

459
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:29,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei!</font>

460
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:30,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Hapus dulu!</font>

461
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:48,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan kesana! Jangan!</font>

462
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:49,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan!</font>

463
00:35:56,940 --> 00:35:58,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Berarti...</font>

464
00:35:59,610 --> 00:36:04,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ahjussi</i> yang juga bisa menjelajah waktu bersama So Joon?</font>

465
00:36:06,930 --> 00:36:10,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Juga yang membantu aku dan So Joon berjumpa?</font>

466
00:36:12,790 --> 00:36:14,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, benar.</font>

467
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf mengatakan ini.</font>

468
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:22,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Terlalu menyakitkan mengatakannya.</font>

469
00:36:23,730 --> 00:36:24,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma Rin.</font>

470
00:36:27,180 --> 00:36:29,650
<font color=#FFFF00>So Joon mungkin tidak akan kembali.</font>

471
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:33,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, dia tidak bisa kembali.</font>

472
00:36:34,450 --> 00:36:36,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, um...</font>

473
00:36:36,750 --> 00:36:40,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...So Joon mengambil keputusan itu dengan sadar penuh akan resikonya.</font>

474
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:41,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak kembali?</font>

475
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:45,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Katanya kau bisa ke masa depan juga.</font>

476
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:49,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak bisakah menemukan dia?</font>

477
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:53,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Cukup caritahu kapan dan dimana dia.</font>

478
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:55,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia terluka?</font>

479
00:36:55,630 --> 00:36:58,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia tidak kembali?
Tidak bisakah menemukan dia?</font>

480
00:36:58,870 --> 00:37:00,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada.</font>

481
00:37:02,070 --> 00:37:03,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah mencarinya, tidak ada.</font>

482
00:37:06,300 --> 00:37:09,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sungguh minta maaf harus mengatakannya.</font>

483
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:12,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

484
00:37:12,380 --> 00:37:16,740
<font color=#FFFF00>...So Joon tidak akan bisa kembali.</font>

485
00:37:16,740 --> 00:37:18,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, kau...</font>

486
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:21,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

487
00:37:22,610 --> 00:37:24,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...harus menerima realita itu.</font>

488
00:37:24,710 --> 00:37:26,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Mulailah hidup baru.</font>

489
00:37:28,730 --> 00:37:29,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

490
00:37:30,650 --> 00:37:32,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tiba-tiba muncul di depanku.</font>

491
00:37:33,830 --> 00:37:36,410
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku akrab dengan So Joon."</font>

492
00:37:36,410 --> 00:37:38,410
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku tahu masa depan."</font>

493
00:37:38,410 --> 00:37:42,170
<font color=#FFFF00>"So Joon tidak bisa kembali."
Aku harus menerimanya begitu saja?</font>

494
00:37:42,170 --> 00:37:44,460
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku tidak akan menunggunya."
Begitu?</font>

495
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:46,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

496
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:48,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau muncul tiba-tiba setelah 20 tahun!</font>

497
00:37:48,910 --> 00:37:51,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan, apa yang sekarang kau katakan?</font>

498
00:37:53,020 --> 00:37:54,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Menyelamatkanku sekali...</font>

499
00:37:54,970 --> 00:37:57,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir lantas berhak meruntuhkan langitku?</font>

500
00:37:57,180 --> 00:38:00,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menyuruhku melakukan ini dan itu.
Apa hakmu?</font>

501
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:05,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa melihat masa depan dengan jelas.</font>

502
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:08,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Mestinya hari itu kau menyelamatkan So Joon, bukan aku!</font>

503
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:12,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang tahu segalanya!</font>

504
00:38:12,460 --> 00:38:15,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau membiarkan So Joon sendirian? Kenapa!?</font>

505
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin So Joon.</font>

506
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:29,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Temukan dia sekarang!</font>

507
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:40,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamatkan aku, selamatkan aku....</font>

508
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:55,920
<font color=#FFFF00>So Ri.</font>

509
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

510
00:38:59,290 --> 00:39:00,680
<font color=#FFFF00>So Ri, bangunlah.</font>

511
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:04,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Aish...</font>

512
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Sialan.</font>

513
00:39:47,530 --> 00:39:51,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau terus saja teriak?</font>

514
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:59,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya kau butuh psikiater.</font>

515
00:40:01,450 --> 00:40:03,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ketakutan.</font>

516
00:40:04,270 --> 00:40:06,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku jadi mimpi buruk.</font>

517
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:09,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak percaya ini.</font>

518
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bahkan menculik Ma Rin.</font>

519
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:21,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kalau terjadi sesuatu yang buruk?</font>

520
00:40:22,610 --> 00:40:25,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga tidak tahu harus bilang apa.</font>

521
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak akan kemari membunuhku, 'kan?</font>

522
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:34,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei. Ayo kabur!</font>

523
00:40:35,430 --> 00:40:37,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku juga?</font>

524
00:40:37,310 --> 00:40:39,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku terlalu takut, tidak bisa sendirian.</font>

525
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:42,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo melarikan diri bersama, So Ri-<i>ah</i>.</font>

526
00:40:43,810 --> 00:40:44,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

527
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:58,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak sanggup menjawabnya.</font>

528
00:40:58,240 --> 00:41:02,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Jawab saja. Pasti ada yang ingin dia katakan.</font>

529
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:07,200
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Bap Soon]</i></font>

530
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh?</font>

531
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:13,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Gun Sook-<i>ah</i>.</font>

532
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:17,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sudah dengar semuanya dari kantor polisi.</i></font>

533
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:19,380
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau tidak apa-apa?</i></font>

534
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:22,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Soal kecelakaan So Joon...</font>

535
00:41:23,550 --> 00:41:25,450
<font color=#FFFF00>...siapa saja yang tahu?</font>

536
00:41:25,450 --> 00:41:27,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sejauh ini, hanya So Ri.</i></font>

537
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:33,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Mulai sekarang, yang terjadi pada So Joon adalah rahasia.</font>

538
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:36,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh? Kenapa?</font>

539
00:41:36,490 --> 00:41:38,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tolonglah, demi aku.</i></font>

540
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Beritahu So Ri untuk diam juga.</font>

541
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:45,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan biarkan dia memberitahu Ibuku.</font>

542
00:41:47,690 --> 00:41:49,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan itu padanya.</font>

543
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:52,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Juga, kau jangan beritahu orang lain lagi, oke?</font>

544
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:57,070
